OL,3,CBack in troubled water: Has P&O gone
OL,4,Crogue again?
OL,6,FConcerns are growing after P&O's
OL,7,Fauditor quits, with their accounts now
OL,8,Fseven months overdue, as ITV News
OL,9,FBusiness and Economics Editor Joel
OL,10,FHills reports
OL,12,FMPs are threatening to formally summon
OL,13,Fthe chief executive of P&O Ferries to
OL,14,Fparliament unless the company can
OL,15,Fexplain why it has failed to file
OL,16,Faccounts on time.
OL,18,FThe accounts of P&O Ferries Division
OL,19,FHoldings Limited for the year ending
OL,20,FDecember 31 2023, are seven months
OL,21,Foverdue.
