OL,3,CBack in troubled water: Has P&O gone
OL,4,Crogue again?
OL,6,FCompany accounts provide a snapshot of
OL,7,Fa firm's financial health. If a
OL,8,Fcompany delays or seeks to avoid
OL,9,Ffiling, it leaves investors,
OL,10,Fcreditors, suppliers, staff and
OL,11,Fcustomers in the dark.
OL,13,FFailure to disclose on time is a legal
OL,14,Foffence, can undermine trust in the
OL,15,Fbusiness and raises questions about
OL,16,Fboth how a company is being managed
OL,17,Fand its solvency.
OL,19,FMP Liam Byrne says he will seek to
OL,20,Fcall P&O before parliament
