OL,3,CBack in troubled water: Has P&O gone
OL,4,Crogue again?
OL,6,F"A company can't be safe unless it is
OL,7,Ffinancially sound. And we don't know
OL,8,Ftoday that P&O is financially sound
OL,9,Fbecause they are so late in filing
OL,10,Ftheir accounts," Liam Byrne told ITV
OL,11,FNews.
OL,13,FHe added: "We've been very clear with
OL,14,FP&O's management that we will seek to
OL,15,Frecall them before parliament to
OL,16,Fexplain what on earth is going on if
OL,17,Fthey cannot put on the table some good
OL,18,Fanswers, and fast."
