OL,4,Crogue again?
OL,6,FKPMG and P&O have chosen not to
OL,7,Frespond to Richard Murphy's comments.
OL,9,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for P&O
OL,10,FFerries said: "We thank KPMG for their
OL,11,Fservices as our auditors, P&O Ferries
OL,12,Fis focused on filing our 2023 accounts
OL,13,Fas soon as possible.
OL,15,F"The business is making a strong
OL,16,Frecovery. We have introduced two state-
OL,17,Fof-the-art hybrid vessels on the
OL,18,FEnglish Channel, opened a new North
OL,19,FSea route and expanded our fleet, and
OL,20,Fare now on the path to operational
OL,21,Fprofitability."
